headline: Morgan Stanly Lowers Target Price on Las Vegas Sands (LVS) to $66 Due to Weak Macau Results
summary: Las Vegas Sands Corp. (NYSE:LVS) is one of the 14 Best Consumer Discretionary Stocks to Buy Right Now. On February 11, Morgan Stanley trimmed its target price on Las Vegas Sands by 1.5% to $66 (from $67), but kept its Equal Weight call on the stock.
